		<div class="article-header__text-wrap">
			<h1 class="article-header__heading" itemprop="headline">Port of Portland approved for federal grant that will double freight capacity</h1>
			<p class="article-header__description" itemprop="description">The $7.7 million project, subject to congressional review, is part of the International Marine Terminal enhancement.</p>		</div>
	</div>

	
